title: If I Don’t Die Soon, I Will Rule The Demon Realm
description: If I Don’t Die Soon, I Will Rule The Demon Realm Manhua A legendary human warrior, vanquished in a brutal confrontation with the demonic forces, is granted a second chance at life. Paradoxically, he awakens as a member of the very race he had sworn to destroy. To reclaim his humanity, he must embrace the irony of his existence and seek a fatal end. However, as he dances with death, he uncovers a sinister plot that threatens both worlds… 再不死我就统治魔界了
